      • joinSolve

        boolean joinSolve()
                  throws IloException

        Waits for the solve operation associated with this handle to complete.

        In other words, this method blocks until the corresponding solve completes.

        Throws:
        IloException
        Returns:

        The value returned by the associated solve.
